data.description: Currently under contract, Seller will consider Back-up offers. This home is a must see.... New pictures!  Many renovations, freshly painted, new carpet and loving care to a wonderful pool in your back yard!!! Pool and Pool Deck refinished, new patio and patio cover, new garage door, installed solar panels, soft water and whole house filtration system and renovated Master Bath and closet all completed in 2021. New appliances also in 2021. Solar panels ($45K cost to install) are huge power savings!!! You don't want to miss this one!!! Buyer to verify all pertinent property info.
